project_descr: The project is expected to restore and maintain forest cover and watershed stability functions while providing for sustainable livelihoods and ecosystem services in the Upper Prek Thnot Watershed.

outputs.output_descr: Reduced erosion and improved soil and water retention in degraded areas in Aural and Phnum Sruoch districts of Kampong Speu province.

project_title: collaborative management for watershed and ecosystem
